  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the proportion of use of complementary and
      alternative medicine (CAM) in patients with inflammatory bowel disease (IBD). In addition,
      the reason for, and satisfaction with use of CAM.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
